net.kuujo.vertigo.cluster

Class XyncCluster

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.kuujo.vertigo.cluster.XyncCluster
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cluster

    public class XyncCluster
extends Object
implements Cluster
    Xync cluster implementation.

    The Xync cluster is backed by the custom Xync platform manager and Hazelcast data structures via the Vert.x event bus. When running the remote cluster the Vert.x instance must have been run with the custom Xync platform manager.

    Author:
    Jordan Halterman
